e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"catgirl"},{"pid":"3a0b6c45df04f0343b33e1b884778b99d17c8ec8","tid":1767910,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:16:10.000Z","msg":"樓豬一定係豬閪"},{"pid":"9a46fbb7c3922e850c998d46e2dadf3097e4452f","tid":1767910,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13a19163230f7fee900096c5380918369c0f8e4e","tid":1767910,"uid":66754,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T19:21:43.000Z","msg":"睇完即刻諗起鄭少秋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4826d575c827f6ba47ba53c3f2a6374fe56e577","tid":1767910,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a0b6c45df04f0343b33e1b884778b99d17c8ec8","tid":1767910,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:16:10.000Z","msg":"樓豬一定係豬閪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:20:38.000Z","msg":"I am a boy"},{"pid":"f0f1e0b41c219c4ec8ddabbd594506acb94ca4dc","tid":1767910,"uid":305631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4826d575c827f6ba47ba53c3f2a6374fe56e577","tid":1767910,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a0b6c45df04f0343b33e1b884778b99d17c8ec8","tid":1767910,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:16:10.000Z","msg":"樓豬一定係豬閪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:20:38.000Z","msg":"I am a boy"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:21:49.000Z","msg":"樓豬一定係屌唔到靚女被逼屌豬西"},{"pid":"2170423c22513ab070cef83ffa674c7be7bd6d11","tid":1767910,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abc47d72839bfe18fbb2cda7fd6f50f53fab74b1","tid":1767910,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T08:22:01.000Z","msg":"呢篇不得了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:27:22.000Z","msg":"乜嘢不得了？"},{"pid":"c036c2385333edda729099a5223b6e71157373c6","tid":1767910,"uid":29689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:28:36.000Z","msg":"其實屌<span style=\"color: red;\">男人</span>比屌豬閪威得多<br />\n<br />\n你諗下，啲豬閪由中學開始俾人排住隊扑到上大學，喺大學再俾人輪流扑到出嚟做嘢，個n手閪都唔知有幾多個男人嘅dna，你都只不過係佢扑嘢生涯中嘅一個過客，分手之後幾個月你問返佢都唔記得你碌鳩咩樣<br />\n<br />\n相反，你同個男人扑嘢，你好大機會就係佢一生中第一個進入佢身體嘅男人，就算你中出即飛，五十年後佢都一定仲記得你碌鳩咩樣，記得當日你征服佢嘅每一個動作，因為對佢嚟講你仲係上一個同佢做愛嘅男人，亦都係唯一一個<br />\n<br />\n最重要係，同人講你同男人上床一定威過講你同個豬閪上床。同豬閪上床，唔係靠樣就靠錢，再唔係就靠口才。但係依個世界唔係得你有樣有錢有囗才㗎嘛，你出到嚟同人講你同阿邊個邊個豬閪上過床，人地隨時答你，超！係人都上過啦，有幾巴閉呀！但係如果你同人講你屌過邊個男人，就唔同喇。<br />\n<br />\n正如我頭先所講，同豬閪上床，樣錢口才是但有咁上下就得，但係同男人做愛呢？就要有無比嘅勇氣同膽識，有一種我不入地獄誰入地獄嘅氣慨。依啲男人可以話萬中無一，因為啲人冇靚女/豬閪個閪屌，就寧願閂埋房門對住個mon打飛機。能夠成為萬中無一嘅男人，你話有幾威？"},{"pid":"9f7d2220ccd0496c63c97f3773e41e5d1d8d0274","tid":1767910,"uid":119596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9474dbe5dad775f0f3d14cab87b01ec35a37d19","tid":1767910,"uid":87337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6630d02fc9ac5cbbf3f0fd19d7c78547d59cfd84","tid":1767910,"uid":204917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"613ec6d21547288d292d185661256636f247775f","tid":1767910,"uid":204916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:22:17.000Z","msg":"樓主幾時示範下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想見識下"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T06:15:49.000Z","msg":"你地結婚啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"6位數..係緣份呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47d8f694eeac135a685ea948d968ceb73819892","tid":1767910,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:38:34.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"856818e9bdc944edadb894314812443d37b3a202","tid":1767910,"uid":310468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:45:06.000Z","msg":"你諗下，啲靚女由中學開始俾人排住隊扑到上大學，喺大學再俾人輪流扑到出嚟做嘢，個n手閪都唔知有幾多個男人嘅dna，你